		## Creating an Ansible Inventory ##
		###################################

# Task 1 - Create a seperate work directory and create a file named "inventory"

# Task 2 - Define two groups "dev" and "web"
	a)	Make sure "node1" and "node2" hosts are part of "dev" group
	b)	Make sure "node2" and "node3" are part of "web" group

# Task 3 - Verify the inventory file
	a)	List the hosts in dev group and web group.

	Optionally, You can run verify_inventory.py
	b)	./verify_inventory.py
